{"tid":754977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來唔覺唔覺1984中既「思想罪(Thoughtcrime)」已經無限接近香港","createTime":"2018-07-24T23:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T06:38:05.000Z","uid":16562,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa8f3a2dc88f2fe19cb1e127deb6374dfbac5e3","tid":754977,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"睇到陳浩天事件，香港政府講下都要拉要鎖，完全唔難想像到有一日科技發展可以讀人地心。香港政府會直接讀取陳浩天個腦諗港獨大計再拉佢。<br />\n<br />\n到底香港政府做乜撚野事！而家阿爺打近貿易戰已經好撚唔得閒架啦！邊撚個叫你無事生非呀？仲要用啲咁既理由。刷鞋都咪咁低莊啦!<br />\n<br />\nFYI:<br />\n犯罪思想（英語：Thoughtcrime）是英國作家喬治&middot;歐威爾作品《一九八四》中的新語名詞，是大洋國政府的一個罪名，若有犯罪思想則會犯下思想罪，而不必在言論或行動上定罪。跟此詞相反的是好思想，即被黨稱讚的思想；基於新話簡單二分法的原則，好思想和犯罪思想中間沒有灰色地帶。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;犯罪思想不會導致死亡，犯罪思想本身就是死亡。\t&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc583cf8c9d07fb51de5dfedce6b527684af9754","tid":754977,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f54aca855e50b5e91e142dc7c1000ec086c996e4","tid":754977,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc583cf8c9d07fb51de5dfedce6b527684af9754","tid":754977,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"re